name: Violent Crime, United Kingdom, 2007/08
description: Association of Public Health Observatories publishes data on the recorded crimes of violence against the person to help target policing and crime prevention resources and to reduce the incidence of violent crime. This indicator is defined by recorded violence against the person offenses, crude rate per 1,000 population, all ages, 2007/08, and persons.
